		"txt":"{\"instruction\":[],\"productName\":\"\",\"label\":[{\"TitleName\":\"Try Now\",\"TitleUrl\":\"//autoscaling-console.jdcloud.com/asGroup\"}],\"desc\":\"Auto Scaling is a service that automatically adjusts the scaling of resources based on the service requirements and scaling policy. By setting scheduled task and monitoring alarm policy, users can have adequate resources to ensure stable and sound business operation. During service peak, the VM instances will be increased automatically to ensure the service performance is not affected; for less service demands, the VM instance types will be decreased to save cost. The service is for free, but the resources needed are charged accordingly.\",\"iconUrl\":\"îŸŸ\",\"imageUrl\":\"//jdcloud-portal.oss.cn-north-1.jcloudcs.com/www.jcloud.com/f860d733-2350-4be9-a379-46906921388020181115163516.svg\",\"middleClstag\":\"Products|keycount|MiddleContentSec|62\",\"sectionClstag\":\"Products|keycount|SectionBannerSec|62\"}",
